OL,3,CReview finds Manx Care's 'arm's length
OL,4,Cmodel' may need to be reconsidered
OL,6,FWhile all options are due to be
OL,7,Fdebated in Tynwald, the government say
OL,8,F'the full implementation of Sir
OL,9,FJonathan Michael's recommendations' or
OL,10,Fa 'strengthened partnership between
OL,11,FManx Care and the DHSC' are the 'most
OL,12,Fviable'.
OL,14,FManx Care was originally established
OL,15,Fas an arms-length delivery body in
OL,16,FApril 2021, following a report by Sir
OL,17,FJonathan Michael in 2019.
