OL,3,CReview finds Manx Care's 'arm's length
OL,4,Cmodel' may need to be reconsidered
OL,6,FWithin the report, he made 26
OL,7,Frecommendations and outlined plans for
OL,8,Fa "Manx Care" body, headed by a
OL,9,F"mainly non-executive" board.
OL,11,FHis report also recommended annual
OL,12,Fincreases in funding for health
OL,13,Fservices to meet rising costs, and the
OL,14,Fsetting of budgets on a three-to-five-
OL,15,Fyear basis, rather than annually.
