OL,3,CReview finds Manx Care's 'arm's length
OL,4,Cmodel' may need to be reconsidered
OL,6,FWhile politicians had previously
OL,7,Freaffirmed its support for
OL,8,Fimplementing the recommendations in
OL,9,Fthe Sir Jonathan Michael report in
OL,10,F2023, this latest review suggests the
OL,11,Fcurrent model is 'unsustainable'.
OL,13,FThe DHSC say they have a full response
OL,14,Fand an 'implementation plan' to
OL,15,Fpresent to parliamentary members at
OL,16,Fthe February sitting of Tynwald.
